sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant OfficeAddIn as DocuID Add-in
    participant Backend as Docuid.net
    participant iVALT

    User->>OfficeAddIn: Opens Add-in
    OfficeAddIn->>User: Shows login screen (Mobile Number)
    User->>OfficeAddIn: Enters mobile number and submits
    OfficeAddIn->>Backend: POST /api/auth/login (mobileNumber)
    Backend->>iVALT: Initiate biometric authentication
    iVALT->>User: Sends push notification for verification
    User->>iVALT: Approves via biometrics
    iVALT->>Backend: Authentication successful callback
    Backend->>OfficeAddIn: Returns success with session token
    OfficeAddIn->>Backend: GET /api/documents (with token)
    Backend->>OfficeAddIn: Returns list of documents
    OfficeAddIn->>User: Displays document list
    User->>OfficeAddIn: Clicks on a document to open
    OfficeAddIn->>Backend: GET /api/documents/{docId} (with token)
    Backend->>OfficeAddIn: Returns document content/URL
    OfficeAddIn->>User: Opens document in Office App 